  "title": "test(DynamicWidgets): clearer assertions for widgets",
  "body": "When the assertions for objectContaining fail, they give a whole lot of information that isn't actually useful, as we only want to know the type.\r\n\r\nI therefore changed it to using the snapshot serialiser we have for widgets, and the diffs are much neater when there's the wrong widgets mounted.",
